### CSGOItemDB.com / CSGORequest.com
I am the creator of the open-source API for people who need to get the most accurate prices of all CS:GO items, cheap and expensive. The repository is available [here](https://github.com/andrewda/CSGOItemDB.com).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
